{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And above the ground, there stood a triangular roof, and it was a long thing, about-- I don't know, 20, 30 yards along the roof.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the trench, you walked down into the trench with little steps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on both-- on the shoulders of the trench, right under the roof, there were boards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the boards, there was straw and blankets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was like 35 people lying next to each other one side and 35 people lying on the other side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is where-- how you slept.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On one side was a door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other side was a little window and a little stove.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The stove was where we would sit around in the evening and pick out the lice and throw them into the fire because if one person had lice, everybody had lice.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like in all camps, there was no way to wash anything or launder anything or even wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So pretty soon everybody was just covered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it killed a lot of people because it itches and you're filthy and you scratch and gets infected and you die.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no children officially.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is one of the weird things the way the German mind works.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shortly after we got there, we were told that this is going to be a labor camp that's going to be too hard for children, and all the children should register.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they'll be taken away to be shown how to learn a craft-- you know, locksmithing or, I don't know, carpentry-- for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it sounded perfectly reasonable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So most kids went when the transport came to take them away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me and maybe five or six others didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
